GetClassType.name: GetClassType
GetClassType.description: Get the type of this class.

GetType.name: GetType
GetType.description: Get the type of the current table conditional style.

GetTextPr.name: GetTextPr
GetTextPr.description: Get the set of the text run properties which will be applied to all the text runs within the table which match the conditional formatting type.

GetParaPr.name: GetParaPr
GetParaPr.description: Get the set of the paragraph properties which will be applied to all the paragraphs within a table which match the conditional formatting type.

GetTablePr.name: GetTablePr
GetTablePr.description: Get the set of the table properties which will be applied to all the regions within a table which match the conditional formatting type.

GetTableRowPr.name: GetTableRowPr
GetTableRowPr.description: Get the set of the table row properties which will be applied to all the rows within a table which match the conditional formatting type.

GetTableCellPr.name: GetTableCellPr
GetTableCellPr.description: Get the set of the table cell properties which will be applied to all the cells within a table which match the conditional formatting type.
